'''Michael Dubisch''' is an illustrator who worked on [[West End Games]] Star Wars roleplaying game books ''[[Alien Encounters]]'' and ''[[The Far Orbit Project]]''. He also worked for [[Wizards of the Coast]] on numerous projects such as ''[[The Unknown Regions]]'' and ''[[The Clone Wars Campaign Guide]]'' among others, and designed several miniatures for their line as well. He's the author of the science fiction graphic novel "Weirdling," and co-creator of the award winning comic series, "The People That Melt in The Rain."

